      • hasSingleReferrer

        public boolean hasSingleReferrer(EdObject referrer)
        Checks if the given EdObject is the only one referrer of this EdObject. That is, if the object has only this given editor referrer and no other external or editor referrers.
        Parameters:
        referrer - referrer to test
        Returns:
        true if the referrer is the only referrer of this EdObject
